title: 820-00165 not turning on
message:
If 3V3_S0 is there, 3V3_S4 must also be present.
Start checking diode mode on it.
If good, change U8000; supposing it gets S4_PWR_EN.

Also check voltage on all big coils.
Just for test, remove Q8150.

title: 820-00165 not turning on
message:
"L7630-0,37v"
Check diode mode to ground first.
If good, post U7600 basic voltages; pins 12 & 16.
Be sure R/C7630 and R7631 are good.
